ime":"2019-08-12T12:00:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊客都唔走，一齊屌共狗<br />\n出面嘅人聽現場話，要留！要守！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">國際機場 通宵運作 </span></strong>我哋坐喺度 邊個犯法？有人清場就有全世界睇住 自有國際社會制裁 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑警有報應 暴權閪尻冧</strong></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>黑警還眼 暴權還命</strong></span><br />\n眼呢？命呢？喺機場等你還㗎！<br />\n<br />\n散水嘅淨係識吹風，你哋有乜作為啊？<br />\n出去？<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">出面會安全得過機場？</span></strong><br />\n愛與和平就喺國際機場啊！咁多日和理飛講㗎！<br />\n成班人湧出去青衣同東涌set個field俾人清啊？<br />\n成班人落旺角準備俾人開片啊？<br />\n<br />\n有料嘅唔該做資料整合<br />\n機場附近環境圖，路線，交通，safehouse⋯<br />\n喱啲先至係有所作為<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>打到嚟自會識走</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TxKRgLR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTxKRgLR.jpg&h=f653330d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留得青山在？草都無幾條淨。<br />\n嗰啲明日戰士啊，我等你啊！"},{"pid":"948a25cc714bfebd8a35d84808f9b9f2f1c26727","tid":1457563,"uid":201385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:02:52.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"62a60369dc4c2325a98bb7c1b6ba55fcb26b356a","tid":1457563,"uid":201385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:04:42.000Z","msg":"811"}]}